title: Episode 5 - Goal Setting: Determining your WHY & developing your mission statement
itunes:title: Episode 5 - Goal Setting: Determining your WHY & developing your mission statement
description:
The key to staying motivated on the journey to your goals is to have a strong WHY. It is what will keep you going when times get tough, and show you why you are really pursuing a goal. In this episode we will talk about what your life could like if you do not hit your goals and then we will go over what your life will look like when you do hit your goals. 

Follow me on IG here: @RobDialJr https://instagram.com/robdialjr
